function onTick() thr_in= iN(1) etmp=iN(2) otmp=iN(3) rpm=iN(4) spd=iN(5) oilprs=iN(8) wea=iN(13) alt=iN(10) fprs=iN(11)*1.2 dlt = iN(27) vopn=-iN(12) htcold=iB(23) hthot=iB(31) rep=iB(18) vauto=iB(20) thrpos=iN(9) lvl=iN(14) bst=iB(16) if etmp<otmp then x=otmp else if etmp>=otmp then x=otmp+etmp-5 end end if etmp>40 then x=etmp end a_prs=100-(alt/100)
visco=((2.16893*10^(-8))*x^4-(5.4663*10^(-6))*x^3+(4.48015*10^(-4))*x^2-0.0238*x+1.7854)*(0.7+0.3*englf/100)*(1-dlt)
if rpm>300 and bst then englf=englf-0.0002 hb=20 end if bst then bst1=1.1 else bst1=1 end
x=x+(-(5.1022*10^(-5))*spd^3+0.0084*spd^2-0.5906*spd)*bst1+crb/20+cyl/10-(x-otmp)/6
if rpm<20 then oilprs=0 end oiltemp=x if rpm<100 and cyl>oiltemp then cyl=cyl-0.05 end if rpm<100 and cyl<oiltemp then cyl=otmp+1 end if vauto then vnt=vnt+vopn else vnt=0 end if vnt<0 then vnt=0 end if vnt>1 then vnt=1 end if rpm>100 and thr>0 then cyl=cyl+rpm*(0.1+0.2*thr)*0.0009*bst1 cyl=cyl-(cyl-otmp)*0.0015-(cyl-otmp)*0.0009*vnt-(spd/350)*vnt-rpm*0.02*0.0009 end
if thrpos>0.9 then oiltemp=oiltemp+thr_in*0.25 cyl=cyl+thr_in*0.08 end
if rpm<300 or thr_in<=0 then cyl=cyl-0.05 end
if cyl<otmp then cyl=otmp end if not hthot and htng>0 then htng=htng-0.01 end if hthot and htng<1 then htng=htng+0.01 end if htng<0 then htng=0 end if htng>1 then htng=1 end if cyl>otmp then ht=(cyl/2)*htng*0.8 end
hb=0
if rpm>100 then crb=otmp-20*(1-thr_in)+ht*0.6+hb else crb=otmp end
if rpm>300 then if lvl<30 then cyl=cyl+(30-lvl)/300 end englf=englf-0.0002 if oilprs<rpm/450 then englf=(englf-(0.01)*(rpm/2300)) end icing=icing-crb*0.0006*wea end
if rpm<100 and cyl>0 then icing=icing-cyl*0.05 end
if crb>0 then icing=icing-crb*0.01 end icing=icing-(rpm*thr_in/1000)/6200 if icing>100 then icing=100 end if icing<1 then icing=1 end
fp=1 --(2.28428*10^(-9))*fprs^9+(2.82092*10^(-7))*fprs^8-(1.44632*10^(-5))*fprs^7+(3.98293*10^(-4))*fprs^6-0.00635*fprs^5+0.05891*fprs^4-0.30098*fprs^3+0.7497*fprs^2-0.65786*fprs+0.00115 if fp>1 then fp=1 end if fp<0 then fp=0 end --0 op. pwr=
(a_prs/100) * (englf/500+0.8)/( ((273+crb+15)/273) ) * fp -(icing/130)
if cyl>245 then pwr=pwr-(cyl-245)/225 englf=(englf-(0.00015)*(cyl-245)) end if cyl>270 then englf=(englf-(0.0003)*(cyl-245)) end
thr=thr_in*pwr
if rpm>300 and thr>0.8 and cyl<90 then if math.random(math.ceil(165-cyl))>10 then thr=0 end else thr=thr_in*pwr end if crb>50 then crb=50 end if crb<-50 then crb=-50 end if cyl>300 then cyl=300 end
if englf<2 then broken=true end if rep and englf>2 then englf=englf+0.1 end if rep and broken then englf=englf+0.03 end if englf>99 and broken==true then broken=false end
if englf<0 then englf=0 end if englf>100 then englf=100 end
sN(2,oiltemp) sN(3,cyl) sN(4,thr) sN(5,crb) sN(6,ld) sN(7,englf) sN(8,visco) sN(9,vnt/2) output.setBool(1,broken) end
function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(1, 1, w, h,
"rpm "..tsN(rpm).."\n"..
"weather "..tsN(wea).."\n"..
"dlt "..ts(dlt).."\n".. "oil_visco "..tsN(visco).."\n".. "\n".. "englf "..tsN(englf).."/100".."\n".. "\n".. "vnt_o "..tsB(vopn).."\n".. "vnt "..tsN(vnt).."/1".."\n".. "\n".. "life_drain "..tsN(ld).."\n".. "\n"..
"a_prs "..tsN(a_prs).."\n".. "crb_icing "..tsN(icing).."/100".."\n".. "crb_htng "..tsN(htng).."/1".."\n".. "\n".. "pwr "..tsN(pwr).."\n".. "oil_press_out "..tsN(oilprs).."\n".. "oil_temp_out "..tsN(oiltemp).."\n".. "cyl_temp "..tsN(cyl).."\n".. "crb_temp "..tsN(crb).."\n".. "\n".. "throttle "..tsN(thr) )
end

heat=0 heating=0 icing=1 lifedrain=0 function onTick()
rpm=input.getNumber(2) thr=input.getNumber(1) outtemp=input.getNumber(3) wea=input.getNumber(4) alt=input.getNumber(5) cyl=input.getNumber(6) heatcold=input.getBool(31) heathot=input.getBool(32) life=input.getNumber(7) test1=input.getNumber(16) test2=input.getNumber(17)
if heatcold and heating>0 then heating=heating-0.01 end if heathot and heating<1 then heating=heating+0.01 end if heating<0 then heating=0 end if heating>1 then heating=1 end
if cyl>outtemp then heat=(cyl/2)*heating*0.8 end
if rpm>100 then carb=outtemp-20*(1-thr)+heat else carb=outtemp end
if rpm>300 then icing=icing-carb*0.0003*wea end if carb>0 then icing=icing-carb*0.01 end icing=icing-(rpm*thr/1000)/6400
if icing>100 then icing=100 end if icing<1 then icing=1 end
abspress=100-(alt/100) --5 optimal temp power=(abspress/100)/(((273+carb-5)/273) * (life/500+0.8))-(icing/130)
if cyl>240 then power=power-(cyl-240)/200 end if cyl>260 then lifedrain=(cyl-259)*0.01/40 else lifedrain=0 end
thr_out=thr*power
if rpm>300 and thr>0.7 and cyl<125 then
if math.random(math.ceil(165-cyl))<40 then thr_out=0 end
end
if carb>50 then carb=50 end
if carb<-50 then carb=-50 end
output.setNumber(1,thr_out) output.setNumber(2,carb) output.setNumber(3,lifedrain)
end

vareng = 0
rel=9000 -- >1500 (9000) i=0 lvl=100 lvldrop=0 function tsN(z) return tostring(math.floor(z*1000)/1000) end function onTick()
rpm=input.getNumber(1) life=input.getNumber(2) visco=input.getNumber(3) thr=input.getNumber(4) oiltemp=input.getNumber(5) repair=input.getBool(2) refill=input.getBool(1) bst=input.getBool(16)
if refill then lvl=lvl+0.16 vareng = 65000 end x=rpm press=visco*(-(9.50922*10^(-11))*x^3-(1.0658*10^(-7))*x^2+0.0035*x+0.06)*(lvl/600+0.85)
if lvl<10 then press=press*lvl/10 end
lvldrop=(rpm*press*life/828000)*0.0003
if rpm>300 then lvl=lvl-lvldrop end if bst and rpm>300 then lvl=lvl-0.001 end
if lvl<0 then lvl=0 end if lvl>100 then lvl=100 end
rpmeng = math.floor(rel*2/(thr*input.getNumber(1)+1)) if rpm>1300 then var1 = math.random(1,math.abs(math.ceil(rpmeng*10*(85/oiltemp)*(7/press)))) var2 = math.random(1,rel)
if (var1<4 and var2<4) or (vareng == 65000) then vareng = 65000 fail=true end end if repair==true then vareng = 0 fail=false end
if fail then lvl=lvl-0.01 press=press-(math.random(-10,10)/10) end
if press>7 then lvl=lvl-0.016 end if oiltemp>75 then lvl=lvl-(oiltemp-75)*0.016*0.3/30 end
if press>7.5 then oilprs=7+math.random(0,20)/40 end
output.setNumber(1,press) output.setNumber(2,lvl) output.setBool(2,fail)
end function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(255, 0, 0)
screen.drawTextBox(w/2, 1, w/2, h,
"fail "..tostring(fail).."\n".. "press "..tsN(press).."\n".. "lvldrop*100 "..tsN(lvldrop*100).."\n".. "lvl "..tsN(lvl)
)
end

time=0 timef=0 cyl=0
function onTick() shots=iN(2) thr=iN(1) cyl=iN(3) ext=iB(26) maint=iB(1)
if cyl>270 then time=time+0.016 end if cyl<270 and not fire then time=time-0.1 end if time<0 then time=0 end if maint then time=0 timef=0 fire=false end
rel1 = 8000
vr = math.random(1,rel1) if vr1 < 65000 then vr1 = math.random(1,rel1) end if ((vr1 <10 and vr<10) or (vr1 == 65000)) and cyl>100 and not maint then vr1 = 65000 fire1=true end
if time>30 or fire1 then fire=true val=val+0.004 else val=0 end
if ext and shots>0 then fire=false fire1=false vr1 = 0 time=0 timef=0 val=val-0.004 end
if val>1 then val=1 end if val<0 then val=0 end
if fire then timef=timef+0.016 else timef=0 end
if timef>40 then flare=true thr=0 end
sN(1,(30+math.random(-30,30))/1000) sN(2,1) sN(3,val) sN(4,thr) output.setBool(1,flare)
end

if st==false then on=false end
if not on and not st then t=0 sts=false else
if not st and rpm<iRPM then on=false end if st and not on and rpm<iRPM and ts<1 then ts=ts+.01 sts=true end if st and not on and rpm>=iRPM then ts=ti on=true sts=false end
if on and rpm<(iRPM+200) and ts<1 then ts=ts+.1 end if on and rpm>(mRPM-200) and ts<1 then ts=ts-.1 end
if on and rpm>=iRPM and rpm<=mRPM then t=ti ts=.1 elseif rpm<iRPM or rpm>mRPM then t=ts end
end
tAs=t*afr tFs=t
if temp>20 then fan=true end
output.setNumber(1,tFs) output.setNumber(2,tAs) output.setBool(1,sts) output.setBool(2,fan) end function onDraw() screen.setColor(255,255,255) screen.drawText(1,1,rpm) screen.drawText(1,7,temp) screen.drawText(1,13,t) end

screen.drawRectF(0, 1, (w/2), 7)
end

end
if inst then
screen.drawRectF(0, 17, (w/2), 7)
end if ralt then
